 "remarks": "Palmer Hill! This highly desirable, luxury gated community is located on the Old Greenwich/Stamford border. Fabulous 2 bedroom/2 bath midrise condo with Rare Private Patio! This home has Many Remodeled and Upgraded Features Including Wood Floors throughout, Custom Lighting, 2 Remodeled Baths, a New Water Heater and HVAC System, Custom Hunter Douglas Window Treatments, Alarm System and Many More. See Improvement List. There are custom closets, an open plan, spacious gourmet kitchen with SS appliances and breakfast bar, living/dining room with a gas fireplace, large windows, and a French door to the Rare Private Stone Patio. The spacious primary en-suite bedroom has a custom walk-in closet and renovated bath. The 2nd bedroom with a spacious closet and 2nd renovated bath complete this wonderful home. A new washer and dryer are located within this home. 2 parking spaces are included in the indoor garage, as well as a storage unit and bike room. Amenities include a newly renovated clubhouse, pool, hot tub, fire pit, gym, yoga room above, and business center. This is a Dog Friendly community. Minutes to I95 and Metro North. Move Right In!  Do Not Miss This Home!",
